Package: DCC
Type: Package
Title: Data Cleaning Center for Survey and Assessment Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("WeianData Engineering", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "engineering@weiandata.example"))
Description: Rule-driven, auditable cleaning of survey and assessment
    response data, implementing the WeianData Detect-Execute-Report
    workflow. Version 0.1 provides the input layer: multi-format,
    multi-encoding file reading ('CSV', 'Excel', 'SPSS', 'Stata', 'SAS',
    'Parquet', 'JSON'), the 'dcc_data' container with a provenance chain,
    and level-0 structural diagnostics producing a machine-readable read
    report.
